HSPC Clinical Assert Status Value Set

SELECT SNOMED CT and Intermountain Healthcare HDD code system values.

Copyright Statement: TBD

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://snomed.info/sct
    CodeDisplay
    55561003Active (qualifier value)
    260385009Ruled out (qualifier value)
    261665006Unknown (qualifier value)
    410605003Confirmed present (qualifier value)
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/hspc-clinicalassertstatus
